"{\n  \"correct\": \"no\",\n  \"explanation\": \"The x parameter of the plt.text() function expects a value in data coordinates, which in this case should be a datetime object or a value that can be interpreted as such. The string '2013-01-05' is not automatically interpreted as a datetime object.\",\n  \"patch\": \"17c17\\n< plt.text(\\\"2013-01-05\\\", 0.5, \\\"SAMPLE\\\")\\n---\\n> plt.text(pd.Timestamp(\\\"2013-01-05\\\"), 0.5, \\\"SAMPLE\\\")\\n\"\n}"